msgid ""
"udpxy is an IPTV stream relay, a UDP-to-HTTP multicast traffic relay daemon "
"which forwards multicast UDP streams to HTTP clients."
msgstr ""
"udpxy 是一个 IPTV 流转发工具,作为一个 UDP 到 HTTP 的组播流转发守护进程它将组"
"播 UDP 流转发到 HTTP 客户端。"

msgid "unspecified"
msgstr "未指定"

